columnContent.title: Simplify observability setup
columnContent.description: One-click setup eliminates the overhead of configuring and maintaining third-party log tools.

columnContent.title: Detect and investigate fast
columnContent.description: Eliminate log ingest lag and conduct forensics with full log and event context.

columnContent.title: Minimize downtime
columnContent.description: Spot issues fast and respond in-platform to contain threats and resolve incidents before they escalate.
